        'supporters-bellec-title': "Message from Rear Admiral François Bellec",
        'supporters-bellec-bio': "<strong><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7ois_Bellec\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">François Bellec</a></strong>, rear admiral, author, painter, and former director of the Musée national de la Marine. As a member of the Académie de Marine, he has advanced the appreciation of French maritime explorations and their cartographic heritage.",
